snippet: The chemical weapons watchdog said that Syria had sent nearly two-thirds of its arsenal for destruction, but that it was uncertain if it would meet its deadline.
abstract: Syria has completed delivery of another shipment of chemical weapons for destruction abroad, bringing total to about two-thirds of its arsenal.
lead_paragraph: The chemical weapons watchdog said that Syria had sent nearly two-thirds of its arsenal for destruction, but that it was uncertain if it would meet its deadline.

headline.main: After Delays, Syria Completes Another Shipment of Chemical Arms
headline.print_headline: Syria: More of Chemical Arsenal Sent for Destruction
